    "steam_appid": 2364180,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2364180/extras/ed5b3b5ddd386c80e3a75497fd96ed70.avif?t=1765624805\" width=600 height=102 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Welcome to my home, an enchanted cottage named &quot;<i>The Merry Fairy</i>&quot;, because I am, indeed, quite a merry one. I invited you here to rest and relax. But I must warn you...</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2364180/extras/16f28d5e5f9b18b9eb173fc40aaa04b8.avif?t=1765624805\" width=600 height=100 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >My home is filled with abundance and serenity. There is nothing that will stress you, challenge you or push you towards any goal. All is plentiful and readily available. You need not worry about a thing. Just relax and unwind in this enchanted haven of mine. I've asked the weather to accommodate your wishes, my friends to come by if you need any help or company, and a handful of enchanted candles that will light your space for as long as you wish.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2364180/extras/b270eb7926996eb6ea660b0741db4d74.poster.avif?t=1765624805\" width=426 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2364180/extras/b270eb7926996eb6ea660b0741db4d74.webm?t=1765624805\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2364180/extras/b270eb7926996eb6ea660b0741db4d74.mp4?t=1765624805\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >I also left you a brand new journal that you write your thoughts in and can decorate as you please. I found the art of scrapbook journaling a powerful practice to  master my own magic. Since I sense you might be a magical creature, like me, I think you might find scrapbook journaling as exciting as I did. You may explore my desk as if it were your own, and use any decorations you like! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >I wish you a pleasant stay!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2364180/extras/ae7a6d724156e6d4a2991485a1ccb366.avif?t=1765624805\" width=570 height=135 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
